# |               |                                                                #
# |     R.Pi      |                                                                #
# |               |    I2C                                                         #
# |          i2c-1|--------------------------bus0---                               #
# |               | parent bus     |                                               #
# |_______________|                |                                               #
#                                  |                                               #
#                                  |    I2C child busses                           #
#                              ____|_____                                          #
#                             |          |---bus1---> Sensors (Temp, Press, Humid) #
#                             |   I2C    |---bus2---                               #
#                             |   Mux    |   ...                                   #
#                             |__________|---bus8---> HV source                    #
#                                                                                  #
#**********************************************************************************#
